org.apache.flex.compiler.constants

Interface IMetaAttributeConstants


  • public interface IMetaAttributeConstants
    Constants used in metadata (e.g. [Event(name="click")] and compiler directives (e.g., @Resource(bundle='foo', key='bar')).
